stuff with the * is from the eric gaffney home video and my copy of that is like 10 years old and not too amazing quality-wise (ripplies on the screen at times) but still great shit none the less.  don&#039;t, free fallin, and limb by limb are incomplete just clips of a verse or so. there&#039;s some non live eric craziness in the mix as well. like music videos he made for ladybugs, bridge was you, and others.

tracks 7-16: 6/17/93 lou, jason, eric
tracks 17-25 2/14/95 lou, jason, bob
tracks 26-30 2/13/97 lou, jason, bob
track 31 HBOs reverb. lou, jason, russ

at the end i put some songs from a folk implosion instore performance at newbury comics from 1996:  lofi suicide, natural one, wont back down (johnny cash), waltzin with yer ego, and take a look inside. 

Thanks due to RS and BiA for providing the source DVD.
